            <article class="project-description" id="mygov-description">
              <p>Badges and Points as a Service (BP-SaaS) is a combination of a web service and a forntend plugin created
                for MyGov (Ministry of Electronmics & Information Technology, Govt. of India) to help implement, calcuate
                and manage points and badges for each user in a modular manner for all sub-systems of MyGov. 
              </p>
            </article>
